---
title: Herby Falafel Flatbreads with Halloumi & Sweet Potato Fries and Garlicky Yoghurt
description: The perfect recipe for sharing with friends, our herby falafel flatbreads are home-made, quick and fun to make, plus preparing it from scratch tastes even better!
